DESCRIPTION:
===========
Legendary, award-winning and suspenseful, ALFRED HITCHCOCK PRESENTS set the gold standard for all TV mystery series to come and has remained an indelible part of popular culture. And now, the complete Sixth Season, all 38 episodes, is available on DVD, filled with tales of murder, madness, intrigue and suspense. Featuring an all star cast, re-discover why the series was voted one of "The 100 Best TV Shows of All-Time." In this worldwide DVD debut, guest stars include Walter Matthau, Claude Rains, Peter Falk, Martin Balsam, Leslie Nielsen, Ricardo Montalban, Barbara Bel Geddes, Julie Adams, Keenan Wynn, Ed Platt, Audrey Meadows, Polly Bergen, Dick York, Rip Torn, Joe Flynn and many more...
